{
  "title": "Exclusive Invite: Regen Content Creator Mastermind @ TDF üêë Oct 12-19",
  "slug": "regen-mstrmnd-at-tdf",
  "html": "<p>Hey ReFi fam!</p><p>John Ellison here. It's been a while...</p><p>I wanted to reach out and invite you to a regenerative content creator mastermind I am hosting at <a href=\"https://www.traditionaldreamfactory.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Traditional Dream Factory in Alentejo, Portugal</a> alongside Sam and Luna on October 12-19! We'll have a wide range of studio-quality recording equipment available including 4K cameras, podcast microphones and lighting. Everything that made ReFi Podcast S3 possible, on a regenerative village in development, with a bunch of amazing creators‚Äîfor one week.</p><p>Plus NVC training, delicious farm-to-table food, a Friday-night DJ set and a content creator showcase...</p><p>Don't miss it! üêë</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/x9kg4ebb\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Learn more</a></div><h2 id=\"enter-regen-mstrmind-%F0%9F%A7%A0\">Enter: Regen MSTRMIND üß†</h2><p>Come along with an idea for a podcast, online course or video series and co-work alongside a brilliant community of content creators each contributing to their vision of a regenerative future! If you've been meaning to start a show, or get your voice out into the wild but haven't quite gotten around to it yet, this could be your chance!</p><p>This is not a conference, it's a mastermind. No one is going to hold your hand. You've got the chance to surround yourself with a bunch of content creators doing their own thing and get into flow doing yours. You'll be expected to put your head down and make stuff happen as well as look up and figure out what you can offer to support the mastermind.</p><p>Who knows what will emerge out of this collective, but we've already begun brainstorming how a small group of content creators could get the story of regeneration out into the world, build larger audiences and drive revenue‚Äîtogether...</p><p>I'll be offering sessions on:</p><ul><li>Personal branding</li><li>Leadership storytelling</li><li>Peak performance neuroscience</li><li>Behavior Design</li><li>Generative AI workflows for podcasting and video creation</li></ul><p>Anyone else is welcome to offer sessions in an '<em>unconference</em>' style format: Share what you learn; Ask what you want to know!</p><p>We'll have three delicious home-cooked meals per day plus a whole host of snacks, tea and speciality coffee. Each evening we'll have time to celebrate life with dance, music and conversation or work later into the evening‚Äîwhatever you vibe, regen. It's lightweight, with a content showcase on the final day to get you into gear and creating before the deadline! Plus, we have a badass DJ on Friday October 11th to celebrate with the TDF fam. </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/x9kg4ebb\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Learn more</a></div><h2 id=\"camping-glamping-scholarships-available-%F0%9F%8F%95%EF%B8%8F\">Camping, glamping &amp; scholarships available üèïÔ∏è</h2><p>We've got a few tiers of tickets based upon people's accommodation preferences whether you prefer unzipping the tent and waking up to the birds in the oak trees or would rather lie in a bit longer under shelter inside a bell tent‚Äîwe got you covered! </p><p>We're also carving out a percentage of sales to go towards a scholarship pool for those who need it!</p><h2 id=\"who-is-going-to-be-there-%F0%9F%A4%A9\">Who is going to be there? ü§©</h2><p>So far we've got a solid community at TDF already in place with the residency program fully underway. It only launched a few days ago and yet confirmed participants are stacking up (we only have spots for 10 more)...</p><ul><li>Luke Ram ‚Äî&nbsp;Regenerative Leader &amp; Spiritual Seeker, launching a new podcast</li><li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/emily-broughton-56048194/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Emily Broughton</a> ‚Äî&nbsp;Impact Investment Community Manager at GenerationRE, launching an online course</li><li>Me (obviously) ‚Äî&nbsp;Regenerative Futurist, launching a new podcast &amp; online course</li><li>DJ Khaled (probably not, but maybe <a href=\"https://x.com/jimicohen\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Jimi</a> or <a href=\"https://x.com/owocki\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Owocki</a> will make it instead)</li><li>YOU ü´µ (yalla, LFGrow!) </li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/x9kg4ebb\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Get your ticket!</a></div><h2 id=\"out-of-the-ashes-into-regeneration-%F0%9F%94%A5\">Out of the ashes, into regeneration üî•</h2><p>This is my first official foray out of sabbatical and into the next stage of my career. I'm about to launch a new podcast called \"<a href=\"https://www.regenera.xyz/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Regen<em>era</em> ‚Äî&nbsp;A Journey to The New Earth</a>\" as well as an online course and retreat series called <em>REBIRTH</em>. I have completely revamped my entire life in pursuit of a holistic vision of regeneration and will be spending the next year between different regenerative villages and land-based communities, creating content, hosting retreats and gathering incredible leaders and storytellers! Come join me...</p><p>I've begun sharing a bit about what I've learned in my deep dive into indigenous wisdom on my newsletter Regenera, and am super excited to host a world-renowned indigenous leader named Jyoti Ma (thanks to the ReFi Prague community) at TDF for an exclusive event on November 2nd (stay tuned)!</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/x9kg4ebb\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Learn more</a></div><h2 id=\"dont-miss-the-vibes-at-tdf-in-october-%F0%9F%AA%A9\">Don't miss the Vibes at TDF in October ü™©</h2><p>Even if you can't come to the Regen MSTRMND October 12-19 there are a whole host of amazing events on the schedule:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://www.traditionaldreamfactory.com/events/abela-art-faire-singularity\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/10/image-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"614\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2024/10/image-1.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/10/image-1.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Abela Art Faire, 2024 | Experiential Art &lt;&gt; Regen Communities &lt;&gt; Nature backed economies</span></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://www.traditionaldreamfactory.com/events/empowering-leaders-for-the-climate-transition\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/10/image.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2024/10/image.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/10/image.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><i><em class=\"italic\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Includes the&nbsp;</em></i><i><b><strong class=\"italic\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Permaculture International Certificate</strong></b></i></figcaption></figure><p>These were the vibes at Decompression Week after The Gathering a couple weeks ago üëá</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-video-card kg-width-regular\" data-kg-thumbnail=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/media/2024/10/tdf-vibes-dance_thumb.jpg\" data-kg-custom-thumbnail=\"\">\n            <div class=\"kg-video-container\">\n                <video src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/media/2024/10/tdf-vibes-dance.mp4\" poster=\"https://img.spacergif.org/v1/1280x612/0a/spacer.png\" width=\"1280\" height=\"612\" loop=\"\" autoplay=\"\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" preload=\"metadata\" style=\"background: transparent url('__GHOST_URL__/content/media/2024/10/tdf-vibes-dance_thumb.jpg') 50% 50% / cover no-repeat;\"></video>\n                <div class=\"kg-video-overlay\">\n                    <button class=\"kg-vide