                          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                                <path d=\"M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z\"></path>\n                            </svg>\n                        </button>\n                        <button class=\"kg-video-mute-icon kg-video-hide\" aria-label=\"Mute\">\n                            <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                                <path d=\"M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z\"></path>\n                            </svg>\n                        </button>\n                        <input type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-volume-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"100\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n        </figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/x9kg4ebb\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Get your ticket</a></div><h2 id=\"learn-more-about-tdf-%F0%9F%90%8F-%F0%9F%A5%95\">Learn more about TDF üêè ü•ï</h2><p>If you haven't checked out the amazing work that Sam, Luna and crew are up to at TDF, this amazing video by our friend <a href=\"https://x.com/zkMenno\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Menno</a> of <a href=\"https://x.com/dClimateDAO\" rel=\"noreferrer\">dClimate</a> is well worth the four minutes! üëá</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/btBqOboLdOg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen=\"\" title=\"Join the dream and support a climate resilient regenerative village in Alentejo, Portugal.\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"hope-to-see-you-there-%F0%9F%A4%A0\">Hope to see you there! ü§†</h2><p>Really looking forward to seeing the ReFi fam again almost a year after handing over the Source baton to Monty at ReFi DAO. Hit me up if you have any questions!</p><p>Peace and love,</p><p>John</p><p><a href=\"https://www.regenera.xyz/\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><strong>regenera.xyz</strong></a><br><a href=\"https://x.com/iamjohnellison\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><strong>x.com/@iamjohnellison</strong></a><br><a href=\"https://instagram.com/iamjohnellison\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><strong>instagram.com/@iamjohnellison</strong></a></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/x9kg4ebb?coupon=REFIFAM75\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Get ‚Ç¨75 off Your Ticket</a></div><p>P.S. ‚Äî&nbsp;If you read this far, here's <a href=\"https://lu.ma/x9kg4ebb?coupon=REFIFAM75\">a discount code for ‚Ç¨75</a> off the Regen MSTRMND! Or use ' REFIFAM75' at checkout'. Some of my favorite posts from Regenera over the last six months below üëá</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://www.regenera.xyz/p/from-ashes-to-regeneration?r=1l137j&amp;utm_campaign=post&amp;utm_medium=web\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">From Ashes to Regeneration üî•</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">An odyssey through love, loss, and the vision of a regenerative era. My first post on a new Substack sharing my journey sitting with sacred medicine alongside a group of leaders in Mexico during the OYASƒ´N Awakening Retreat.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/icon/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2Ff4004741-714e-4784-a8d2-c1a8aacb2352-2Fapple-touch-icon-180x180.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Regenera with John Ellison</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">John Ellison</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/thumbnail/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2Fec6e1f0e-21ef-4262-8be8-c43e339498fd_1024x1024.webp\" alt=\"\" onerror=\"this.style.display = 'none'\"></div></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://www.regenera.xyz/p/myths-of-the-regenerative-era-part\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Myths of The Regenerative Era: Part I ‚Äî The Eagle &amp; The Condor</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">What an ancient prophecy from The Americas teaches us about the regenerative age</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/icon/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2Ff4004741-714e-4784-a8d2-c1a8aacb2352-2Fapple-touch-icon-180x180-1.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Regenera with John Ellison</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">John Ellison</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/thumbnail/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2Fe54573a0-9ac8-4f5b-8daa-eadf0fd5ff6e_1280x731.jpeg\" alt=\"\" onerror=\"this.style.display = 'none'\"></div></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://www.regenera.xyz/p/only-love-is-real-ep-coming-soon\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Only Love Is Real ‚Äî EP COMING SOON</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">This demo is an offering: A gift from my heart ‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/icon/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2Ff4004741-714e-4784-a8d2-c1a8aacb2352-2Fapple-touch-icon-180x180-2.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Regenera with John Ellison</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">John Ellison</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/thumbnail/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fvideo_upload-2Fpost-2F149441997-2F72103944-2e54-4168-b35d-971d092f7245-2Ftranscoded-06542.png\" alt=\"\" onerror=\"this.style.display = 'none'\"></div></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://www.regenera.xyz/p/part-ii-the-condors-wisdom-seven\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Part II: The Condor‚Äôs Wisdom ‚Äî Seven Myths for a Regenerative Future</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">How The Indigenous Worldview Can Decolonize Our Minds and Heal Our Planet</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/icon/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2Ff4004741-714e-4784-a8d2-c1a8aacb2352-2Fapple-touch-icon-180x180-3.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Regenera with John Ellison</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">John Ellison</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/thumbnail/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2F41354090-8394-4592-80df-10222f09b9d3_1728x706.jpeg\" alt=\"\" onerror=\"this.style.display = 'none'\"></div></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://www.regenera.xyz/p/awakening-from-the-dream\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Awakening From The Dream</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">What emerged from Shared Dreaming with friends at TDF after The Gathering</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/icon/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fpublic-2Fimages-2Ff4004741-714e-4784-a8d2-c1a8aacb2352-2Fapple-touch-icon-180x180-4.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Regenera with John Ellison</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">John Ellison</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/thumbnail/https-3A-2F-2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com-2Fvideo_upload-2Fpost-2F149219754-2F83390925-2538-451a-814c-b05c1798a495-2Ftranscoded-00001.png\" alt=\"\" onerror=\"this.style.display = 'none'\"></div></a></figure>",
